<reference id="chhead" xml:lang="en-us">
   <title>
      <keyword>chhead</keyword>
   </title>
   <shortdesc>The &lt;<keyword>chhead</keyword>&gt; element is a container inside the &lt;<keyword>choicetable</keyword>&gt; element
that provides specific heading text to override the default <b>Options</b> and <b>Description</b> headings.
The &lt;<keyword>chhead</keyword>&gt; element contains both a <ph>
         <xref href="choptionhd.xml">choptionhd</xref>
      </ph> and <ph>
         <xref href="chdeschd.xml">chdeschd</xref>
      </ph> element
as a pair.</shortdesc>
   <prolog>
